# kidsn-babies-
Welcome to "kidsnbabies"- the kids clothing paradise". We are located at Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. Our online store has a wide range of clothing for your precious little girls and boys. We have gathered a great collection of children clothing from all over the world for both casual and formal occasions.

When our first daughter was born we were so excited, for her first birthday we wanted to buy her the most beautiful dress. We went to so many shops, spent several hours looking for the best one but couldn't find anything that could make us happy. So we started looking on internet. I had done some online shopping for her previously as well and was not happy with all of it. So eventually I searched overseas websites and found a couple of beautiful dresses for my little princess. Then again, for her second, third and fourth birthdays I did shopping from overseas. When other mums asked me about those dresses and we talked how hard here it is to get beautiful and variety of children's clothing for party or daily wear in affordable prices , it gave me an insight that many mums and dads like us struggle to find the best for their little prince and princesses.
